text: The High Commissioner of Malaysia to the Nation of Brunei, the Abode of Peace is the head of Malaysia's diplomatic mission to Brunei. The position has the rank and status of an Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary and is based in the High Commission of Malaysia, Bandar Seri Begawan. ==List of heads of mission== ===High Commissioners to Brunei=== {| class=wikitable !
